cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.CL, cs.PL, cs.CR 

This paper deals with reasoning and abduction in logic theories, which are core topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The use of Answer Set Programming (ASP) as a framework for experimentation suggests that the paper may also belong to the programming languages (cs.PL) category. The application of the approach to plan recognition in natural language understanding (NLU) suggests that the paper may also belong to the computational linguistics (cs.CL) and cryptography and security (cs.CR) categories.
